---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/Default.astro';

const title = 'Contact';
---

<DefaultLayout content={{ title }}>
	<header class="section section--emphasis">
		<div class="content">
			<h1>
				{title}

				<span class="subtitle">Let’s get in touch</span>
			</h1>
			<p>Getting a hold of me is easy. Drop me a line with the links on this page if you’re interested in working together or just to contact me and say “Hi!”</p>
		</div>
	</header>
	<div class="section">
		<div class="content">
			<p>I’m on LinkedIn, Twitter, and Github. Keep track of <a href="https://github.com/Firestorm980/">me on Github</a> to see what side projects I’m working on right now. <a href="https://twitter.com/jonmchristensen">Follow me on Twitter</a> if you like hearing my nerdy thoughts about web, entertainment and other things. Unfortunately, I don’t usually respond to <a href="http://harrypotter.wikia.com/wiki/Owl#Postal_workers">messages by owl</a>.</p>
			<p>If you’re looking for more official things, you can take a look at <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jon-christensen-2768381a/">my LinkedIn profile</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</DefaultLayout>
